# arvo-tensor

L2 fixed-shape tensor wrappers with type-level capacity:
`Array<T, N>` (rank-1), `Matrix<W, N>` (rank-2). `cap_size(c: Cap)`
bridge. `Enumerator` trait with blanket `IntoIterator` impl yielding
`(USize, &T)` for typed iteration. `#![no_std]`, no alloc, stack-only.
Depends on arvo L0 only.
